  # 70 ¿Quien fue el primer Presidente?
    ["Who was the first President?\n1) George Washington\n2) Abraham Lincoln\n3) Benjamin Franklin\n4) James Madison\n5) Thomas Jefferson", "1", "1 - George Washington was the first president of the United States. He began his first term in 1789 & voluntarily resigned from the presidency after two terms.", "rev. 02/16", "Spanish"],

