  # 71 ¿Que territorio compro los Estados Unidos de Francia en 1803?
    ["What territory did the United States buy from France in 1803?\n1) Mississippi\n2) Louisiana\n3) Tennessee\n4) Maryland\n5) Alabama", "2", "2 - In 1803, the US bought the Louisiana Territory from France for $15 million and was the largest acquisition of land in American history.", "rev. 02/16", "Spanish"],

